<br>
Bottom line is, you avoid LD death and can kite with 3 dots.  Ever have some lag and have selos drop....only to have lag settle down and find yourself at half or bellow health ?  sow potions takes care of that.....just make sure you are on auto run.<br>
<br>
Neesha, since your bard is not of level to twist chants of fulfills, the answer to your question is what Leo said.  almost all bard songs have a 3 tick duration...and if I am not mistaken, a tick is 3 sec long.  <br>
<br>
So essentially you can twist Denon's Distruptive Discord (with brass instrument), Chords of Dissonance (with Lute) and Hymn of Restoration (also with Lute)<br>
<br>
This is a very effective way to solo through some levels especially LoIO (if you don't mind shutting off ooc and shout channel)<br>
<br>
